        "name": "Sudden Transposition",
        "type": "stat_block_section",
        "text": "You wrench the targets off their feet, forcefully teleporting them within the area. The creatures must each be able to fit in their new space, and their positions must be unoccupied, entirely within the area, and in your line of sight. Each target attempts a Fortitude save.",
